OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774102277
OL,3,CNearly a ton of cocaine worth #75m
OL,4,Chidden in pallets of bananas seized at
OL,5,Cdocks
OL,7,FAlmost a ton of cocaine worth
OL,8,F#75million which was hidden among
OL,9,Fpallets of bananas has been seized at
OL,10,FSouthampton Docks.
OL,12,FThe Class A drugs were discovered
OL,13,Fafter the container they were in had
OL,14,Fsailed from Nicaragua via Panama to
OL,15,Fthe UK.
OL,17,FActing in partnership with the
OL,18,FNational Crime Agency, Border Force
OL,19,Fofficers opened it and found 943kg of
OL,20,Fcocaine with a street value of around
OL,21,F#75m among pallets of bananas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
