PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774102277
OL,3,CNearly a ton of cocaine worth #75m
OL,4,Chidden in pallets of bananas seized at
OL,5,Cdocks
OL,7,FTwo men - Daniel Dumitru, 37, of
OL,8,FReginald Road, Smethwick, West Mids,
OL,9,Fand Andrew Smyth, 46, of West Park
OL,10,FGardens, Prenton, Merseyside, have
OL,11,Fbeen charged with importing Class A
OL,12,Fdrugs.
OL,14,FNCA Branch Commander Saju Sasikumar
OL,15,Fsaid: "This is a massive amount of
OL,16,Fcocaine which was destined for the
OL,17,Fstreets of the UK.
OL,19,F"The supply of Class A drugs badly
OL,20,Fdamages society by bringing violence
OL,21,Fand addiction to our communities.
